{"tid":1468781,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【民意戰線】對唔住，阻到您！","createTime":"2019-08-13T20:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T15:27:58.000Z","uid":111354,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"69fe7d5ee47a05208a21eb0ae837be53cb449170","tid":1468781,"uid":111354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:50:47.000Z","msg":"拿 第一句講明先 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔割蓆 核爆都唔割蓆</span></span><br />\n但唔代表唔可以賽後檢討<br />\n尋日做法唔完美 可以進步 <br />\n<br />\n要注意嘅係唔少外媒聽日報嘅第一樣嘢就係呢樣<br />\n加上遊客唔滿意 事關香港聲譽<br />\n嗰澳洲佬上埋黨報<br />\n對家一定如獲至寶 盡情炒作<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以坐以待斃！！！<br />\n<br />\n有見及此 我同幾個網友寫左份懶人道歉信<br />\n簡單5點解釋點解唔割蓆、點解要抗爭<br />\n原理同稅務大樓follow up一樣 <br />\n<br />\n注意！！道歉唔係為示威道歉<br />\n係為阻到人道歉<br />\n我哋要同佢哋解釋：示威阻到你唔好意思 但係為左白色嘅明天 係必須嘅！！<br />\n要誠懇有禮咁同 中立  同  淺藍 講：阻到您，對唔住，SORRY！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rc5dF1y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRc5dF1y.png&h=28098805&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z9drgzX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9drgzX.png&h=009c4873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望連登上下可以係各大報章嘅post下面轉貼道歉信<br />\n貼滿各區連儂牆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話print 出黎派比街坊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">A4版大大隻 唔怕老花睇唔到:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://we.tl/t-7w7FqVzaJ5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwe.tl%2Ft-7w7FqVzaJ5&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=def05a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://we.tl/t-7w7FqVzaJ5</a><br />\n<br />\n希望我哋嘅follow up可以保住世界最高汁AI抗爭嘅聲譽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油！！！！<br />\n<br />\n雖然我們對為市民帶來不便感到抱歉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但請別忘記，昨晚的始作俑者是誰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X08e94v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX08e94v.png&h=85aa5ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/044536_ff7ba130167e34f534dbc3b9ad9bf7f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F044536_ff7ba130167e34f534dbc3b9ad9bf7f3.png&h=199d23e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(Credit to 我要攬炒巴打）"},{"pid":"43143efab23d2a9c366adc2a3d4108ba5503cdbe","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:51:55.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fb5a8261fab8c12b1db9bcff779e7265536f25","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:52:25.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18d22dd7f24d854e102cc9b1455c8c87fc1d2d2","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:52:56.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2f159661aba9a7f30bc351fc5a4fedcdad1da4","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:53:27.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643bacf730b8854000ca10d6ee35168f8d17a84c","tid":1468781,"uid":272892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:53:28.000Z","msg":"我們在這裏 謹代表不負責任的香港政府 向旅程受阻的各國旅客致歉<br />\n並促使林鄭政府回應示威者訴求"},{"pid":"747e5c2f6aafc5c685da2377467586c4f80b25f4","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:53:57.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1130a37695932a157eb4c9f5bf921880b2332e9","tid":1468781,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:53:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7a3e460d3268ffaa3b64db23f4fce814d112fd30","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:54:21.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191876ff421f14ce9c1f9eea205c6580de1f960f","tid":1468781,"uid":111354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:55:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c5aee1cff229b49bd0e5c6c01f9599021f7bcffe","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:55:06.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04ac443e3dc26923c5313b9552073f6bd3c669e","tid":1468781,"uid":111354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:55:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fbd150a791543645b9e317b742fb1d918036af7c","tid":1468781,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:55:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不割蓆，唯要改進</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n813 之事其實情有可原，因為比人射爆隻眼真係好嬲，我地大家絕對唔會割蓆，但我地亦都要持續去改進，希望運動可以更上一層樓邁向成功之日，我地要一齊尊重，正如人人平等冇話邊個大啲有得話事啲，有咩提議大家投票決定，呢個亦係民主真諦，我地亦要每日一齊去檢討得失，正如人人都會有失誤嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n古今中外所以社會運動總會有失誤嘅時候，呢個係好自然亦可常見嘅事，可貴之處就係識得自省，至少我覺得813 呢日明顯唔係end game 嘅一日，如果有朝一日真係end game 嘅係一戰竟全功嘅時候咁到時我地做乜嘢都可以，但喺呢一日來臨之前嘅過程上，我地唔可以急，仇恨係要記住因為係一股動力，但亦要避免比仇恨支配行動，古今歷史上每一場運動係要好長時日去完成，而且過程係一定會出現爭拗，除咗不割蓆不分化，自省改進，檢討得失，去改善下一步行動亦係成功之道。<br />\n<br />\n已經發生咗嘅事我地冇辦法再去改變，比人射爆隻眼真係好嬲所以我地亦冇資格去怪責甚至割蓆，但我好希望呢場運動可以成功，而呢場運動其中一樣重要嘅係自己要有一個自省精神，一旦出現失誤就要反省，反省完就要檢討，吸取教訓，下次再可以做好啲，人數亦會keep住多，人多就可以贏，如果出現失誤唔去檢討，唔尊重對方互相指罵，只會不斷重複失誤，人數會變少，最後重演2014年雨革失敗歷史。<br />\n<br />\n完美係一種永遠唔會達到但可以追求嘅哲學，所以我地只有不斷改善自己，互相指正，幫大家補鑊，一齊進步，一齊向成功之日進發，煲底之日我地仲要一齊慶祝"},{"pid":"8b00a98e15c3f72319ea16c1e42824fea852476d","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:55:52.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0235ae0b694127787ba0f5ba9739da128f3b132","tid":1468781,"uid":253377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:56:05.000Z","msg":"好鍾意最後果段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68ce7fe4b1a0d6af1fb2a539a3daed0c633eaa2","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:56:37.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc56610f6274870b2643ea0238fae67549f495c","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:57:22.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c818c6c770268eddd0a72956c187274a6e080e0","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:58:07.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951ada441316bd6c2ba8277b34d50447d46ae4e6","tid":1468781,"uid":258933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:58:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"97a6084ceaf7e48b168aef91ab9008b199af8029","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:58:52.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6725a3f09edb322f37e91557f68780d341ec2be1","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:59:37.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ab44a57db7bddae0565092cca536764a001db4","tid":1468781,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:00:22.000Z","msg":"恭喜共匪柒出國際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\