frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c36e11e945bbb2a2082b1493d85401c9926c25","tid":1468781,"uid":1581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:04:29.000Z","msg":"仲有機場一定和理非，個位置亦都唔適合勇武<br />\n一封橋就滅團<br />\n<br />\n唔夠人塞未文宣算，贏國際形象最緊要"},{"pid":"7a2c2e623e9ea6bddc5ea32d617f9c860c8b83bc","tid":1468781,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:14:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ad6dd273766325d8a51bafbfcad9ce0c72f7c42d","tid":1468781,"uid":130262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:57:49.000Z","msg":"對唔住，阻到你！"},{"pid":"71f7e08b3fba6cd6dab0bda8d52beda611693801","tid":1468781,"uid":156968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0891097860e20a8b75a06bc7edb62a96f95a4556","tid":1468781,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:59:30.000Z","msg":"唔完美 可接受 要改善"},{"pid":"35fba5bf2ccc1e57b233ffbec14e41d6f2f1813c","tid":1468781,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:59:55.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1e1bab64dd9f8a7a8d97c4b01abdbbd18d1426ec","tid":1468781,"uid":49083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:03:01.000Z","msg":"抗爭者多數十幾二十碎，而對手係警黑政聯盟，抗爭者經歷過黑暗唔多，亦唔明白世途險惡<br />\n<br />\n因為無大台，佢地好多時係即場做決定，而佢地唔知岩定唔岩，亦唔似我睇住電視過幾分鐘先講應該點點點做，更莫講話身邊極多鬼<br />\n<br />\n有時佢地做錯決定我只恨佢地唔夠對家玩，有得教米教佢囉，點解要割？"},{"pid":"8c91ef90d982de6946e2b91dd100bb23c7ecb3b7","tid":1468781,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:06:02.000Z","msg":"I support and approve this message"},{"pid":"711608fd05820eed4fab703e381a53553ed89240","tid":1468781,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfe99149e1a11f871d7a91d1896d0aaef53e525","tid":1468781,"uid":241501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:11:05.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"53869414cb5994dc7dc0752d08fd54de6ac42984","tid":1468781,"uid":50901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69fe7d5ee47a05208a21eb0ae837be53cb449170","tid":1468781,"uid":111354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:50:47.000Z","msg":"拿 第一句講明先 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔割蓆 核爆都唔割蓆</span></span><br />\n但唔代表唔可以賽後檢討<br />\n尋日做法唔完美 可以進步 <br />\n<br />\n要注意嘅係唔少外媒聽日報嘅第一樣嘢就係呢樣<br />\n加上遊客唔滿意 事關香港聲譽<br />\n嗰澳洲佬上埋黨報<br />\n對家一定如獲至寶 盡情炒作<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以坐以待斃！！！<br />\n<br />\n有見及此 我同幾個網友寫左份懶人道歉信<br />\n簡單5點解釋點解唔割蓆、點解要抗爭<br />\n原理同稅務大樓follow up一樣 <br />\n<br />\n注意！！道歉唔係為示威道歉<br />\n係為阻到人道歉<br />\n我哋要同佢哋解釋：示威阻到你唔好意思 但係為左白色嘅明天 係必須嘅！！<br />\n要誠懇有禮咁同 中立  同  淺藍 講：阻到您，對唔住，SORRY！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rc5dF1y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRc5dF1y.png&h=28098805&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z9drgzX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9drgzX.png&h=009c4873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望連登上下可以係各大報章嘅post下面轉貼道歉信<br />\n貼滿各區連儂牆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話print 出黎派比街坊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">A4版大大隻 唔怕老花睇唔到:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://we.tl/t-7w7FqVzaJ5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwe.tl%2Ft-7w7FqVzaJ5&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=def05a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://we.tl/t-7w7FqVzaJ5</a><br />\n<br />\n希望我哋嘅follow up可以保住世界最高汁AI抗爭嘅聲譽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油！！！！<br />\n<br />\n雖然我們對為市民帶來不便感到抱歉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但請別忘記，昨晚的始作俑者是誰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X08e94v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX08e94v.png&h=85aa5ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/044536_ff7ba130167e34f534dbc3b9ad9bf7f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F044536_ff7ba130167e34f534dbc3b9ad9bf7f3.png&h=199d23e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(Credit to 我要攬炒巴打）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"口號叫極都係唔肯用外語<br />\n正確做法係要本地新聞都只影到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外語口號</span>啊<br />\n入去唔係圍爐啊"},{"pid":"507c21e406226192273296d1c250ca27efee8cbd","tid":1468781,"uid":57701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"210ce4241db0b8b45dd803dcf923c97e61389077","tid":1468781,"uid":103573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:21:45.000Z","msg":"道歉日必用"},{"pid":"8ca054b64d002807ef1a5346e59cd7b0676746c7","tid":1468781,"uid":81652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"真係要搞眾籌登頭版道歉"},{"pid":"f6c3fb6a0b136de38da9661789bbee3f3c69036a","tid":1468781,"uid":62881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:23:07.000Z","msg":"唔割唔割"},{"pid":"bde59320c40da3a8aef44c047aa405b299026dcb","tid":1468781,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:31:53.000Z","msg":"經過812同813我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{